.Ss EXODUS-SPECIFIC ARGUMENTS
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width "--concatenate" -compact
.It Fl d Ar file
.It Fl -datafile Ar file
Specifies the exodus file to use for training. The
trees are written to a
.Ar file
but with the extension replaced by
.Ar .trees .
.It Fl V Ar name
.It Fl -class-var Ar name
Use the variable named
.Ar name
as the class definition.
.It Fl C Ar file
.It Fl -class-file Ar file
Use
.Ar file
as the class configuration file. The 
.Fl -class-var
command line argument overrides the class variable as defined in the class-file. See the
.Sx FORMATS
section for details.
